data.description: Discover your dream home in Lonesome Oak Subdivision! This beautiful residence boasts 3 bed, 2 full bath, a great room with fireplace, and laminate flooring. The carpeted bedrooms include a master with walk-in closet and tray ceiling. Enjoy a spacious kitchen, fenced-in backyard, and newly built covered porch. Community pond access and plenty of storage complete this home. Call to schedule a showing today.
